Package: causalwiz
Type: Package
Title: Tools for Causal Inference Analysis and Visualization
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Carmine Minichini
Maintainer: Carmine Minichini <carmine.mnc@gmail.com>
Description: A comprehensive toolkit for causal inference analysis in R. 
    Provides functions for causal identification, estimation of treatment effects,
    sensitivity analysis, and visualization of causal relationships. 
    Implements various methods including propensity score matching, 
    inverse probability weighting, instrumental variables, and 
    difference-in-differences approaches. Features intuitive visualization 
    tools for causal diagrams and treatment effect estimates.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
